    "<div style=\"border:3px solid purple; padding:20px; border-radius:6px;\">\n",
    "\n",
    "  <h1 style=\"margin-top:0;\">Mobile Plan Classification Project</h1>\n",
    "\n",
    "  <p>\n",
    "    Telecommunication companies offer different mobile service plans designed to meet the needs of various customers.\n",
    "    In this dataset, users are subscribed to either the Smart plan or the Ultra plan.\n",
    "    The company wants to improve its ability to recommend the most suitable plan to users based on their monthly usage behavior.\n",
    "  </p>\n",
    "\n",
    "  <p>\n",
    "    This project applies machine learning classification techniques to analyze customer behavior and predict which mobile plan\n",
    "    a user is most likely to choose. The dataset includes variables such as the number of calls made, minutes used, messages sent,\n",
    "    and internet data consumption.\n",
    "  </p>\n",
    "\n",
    "  <p>\n",
    "    By identifying patterns in these usage features, this project builds a predictive model that can automatically classify users\n",
    "    into the most appropriate plan.\n",
    "  </p>\n",
    "\n",
    "  <h2>Project Objective</h2>\n",
    "  <p>\n",
    "    The objective of this project is to develop a machine learning model that accurately predicts whether a user should be assigned\n",
    "    to the Smart plan or the Ultra plan based on their monthly usage statistics.\n",
    "  </p>\n",
    "\n",
    "  <p>To accomplish this objective, the project will:</p>\n",
    "\n",
    "  <ul>\n",
    "    <li>Explore and understand the dataset through exploratory data analysis (EDA)</li>\n",
    "    <li>Split the data into training, validation, and test datasets</li>\n",
    "    <li>Train multiple machine learning models, including:\n",
    "      <ul>\n",
    "        <li>Decision Tree</li>\n",
    "        <li>Random Forest</li>\n",
    "        <li>Logistic Regression</li>\n",
    "      </ul>\n",
    "    </li>\n",
    "    <li>Tune model parameters to improve performance</li>\n",
    "    <li>Evaluate model accuracy using validation and test datasets</li>\n",
    "    <li>Perform a sanity check using a baseline model</li>\n",
    "    <li>Select the model that achieves the best predictive performance while meeting the project requirement of at least 0.75 accuracy</li>\n",
    "  </ul>\n",
    "\n",
    "  <p>\n",
    "    The final model will support data-driven decision-making by enabling automated plan recommendations based on user behavior.\n",
    "  </p>\n",
    "\n",
    "</div>"
   ]
  },
